name: "Google Pixel 3a"
comment: "community device"
description: >
  The Pixel 3a is available in Black, Clearly White, and Purple-ish.
  Powered by a Qualcomm Snapdragon 670 processor and 4 GB of RAM,
  it offers strong value for a Linux-capable phone. It features a
  3,000 mAh battery, a vivid 5.6-inch OLED display, USB Type-C,
  a 3.5 mm headphone jack, and excellent camera quality for its class.
